  "detailed_description": "In the town of St. Olympus, Matthew and his friendly pet spider encounter formidable monsters, which do not like humans or spiders. In your quest to escape the nightmare, you will:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Use tools, weapons, and cunning to defeat enemies, each with different strengths and weaknesses...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/af31fe3d58da94124533dbfce62ad68e.poster.avif?t=1709853888\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/af31fe3d58da94124533dbfce62ad68e.webm?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/af31fe3d58da94124533dbfce62ad68e.mp4?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  Solve challenging puzzles and find important items to help you on your journey...</h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/d8e5dfad77a934f4cf841ab49c97c17e.poster.avif?t=1709853888\" width=600 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/d8e5dfad77a934f4cf841ab49c97c17e.webm?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/d8e5dfad77a934f4cf841ab49c97c17e.mp4?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  Drive with your spider through St. Olympus's underground and work together to defeat the monsters...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/f25374162f7e237c36cf1157e0eced48.poster.avif?t=1709853888\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/f25374162f7e237c36cf1157e0eced48.webm?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885510/extras/f25374162f7e237c36cf1157e0eced48.mp4?t=1709853888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Includes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fully customizable controls</strong><br></li><li><strong>Support for a wide-range of controllers</strong><br></li><li><strong>Unique controller vibration/rumbling effects</strong></li></ul>",
